  "finalSubmissionGuidelines": "<h2><span style=\"font-family:trebuchet ms; font-size:17.333333333333332px\">Challenge Deliverables</span></h2>\n&nbsp;\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial; font-size:14.666666666666666px\">- The updated backend code meeting all the requirements above</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial; font-size:14.666666666666666px\">- No video necessary</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial; font-size:14.666666666666666px\">- Update the </span><a href=\"https://github.com/topcoderinc/BP-Ionic-Heroku/blob/dev/Backend/README.md\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><u>existing deployment guide in MD format</u></a></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial; font-size:14.666666666666666px\">- A live Heroku instance running the updated code base (using the games data in a Postgres database - don&#39;t break this functionality while implementing email)</span></p>\n<span style=\"font-family:arial; font-size:14.666666666666666px\">- An updated postman file demonstrating all API calls to your live Heroku instance (update the existing postman collection / environment files to include the email API calls)</span>",
